tip.text: Wipeout pizza. Came in pairs on Wednesdays.
Cold and fresh. Just the way I like it.
Har  Qiong Gai Burger! Basically prawn paste chicken burger style. Nice moist tasty. The bun is a tad dry. Those are Truffle fries and bits of garlic chips. Lovely.
Coke Zero here taste best at $1.30 in the middle of the night at 26°C and 86% humidity. Just right.
Coke Zero here taste fabulous in the middle of the night with humility of 86% and temperature 26°c. Just right.
Very new and nice environment. The small bungalow face the garden. The toilet is interesting.
Burgers here are excellent. Close to our resort and easy access. Chill out place. We had the Great American and John Wayne.
Soft Shell Crab. Black Pepper Angel hair. Tasty combination.
Nice family atmosphere. Clean villa though a bit old. As usual the monitor lizard makes its appearance at the Nirwana poolside to entertain the kids.
The famous Nasi Lemak which Lee Hsien Loong served to the Indonesian president. Prawn noodles is pretty good too. I personally like the Mee Goreng special.
